title: Manufacturing turnover drop in August - 1.9% (CSB - Central Statistical Bureau)
text: ( Source : CSB - Central Statistical Bureau ) Latest data compiled by the Central Statistical Bureau show thatcompared to July manufacturing turnover1 in August 2015 according to seasonally adjusted data (at current prices) declined by 1.9%.
